title: Rush - Rush Through Time [FIXED] [320k MP3]
description:
Original upload had a clicking error on 2112 Overture - this is the 'fixed' version

Rush Through Time is a compilation album by Rush, released in Europe in 1978 (see 1978 in music). The compilation contained selections from the band's second, third, fourth, and fifth studio albums (Fly by Night, Caress of Steel, 2112, and A Farewell to Kings).. According to Rush drummer Neil Peart, the album was compiled by the German branch of Polygram Records without the band's input.
